      <title>阿波罗的泽尔特表示，私人信贷在经济低迷时期将表现出色</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/private-credit-to-outperform-in-a-downturn-apollo-s-zelter-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿波罗全球管理公司 (Apollo Global Management Inc.) 联席总裁詹姆斯泽尔特 (James Zelter) 在接受彭博电台采访时表示，在经济衰退时期，私人信贷的表现将“远远超过”高收益和杠杆贷款市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/private-credit-to-outperform-in-a-downturn-apollo-s-zelter-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 12:18:23 GMT</pubDate>
